     <body class="background">

       <nav class="navbar navbar-inverse navbar-fixed-top">
         <div class="container">
           <div class="navbar-header">
             <button type="button" class="navbar-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbar" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="navbar">
               <span class="sr-only">Toggle navigation</span>
               <span class="icon-bar"></span>
               <span class="icon-bar"></span>
               <span class="icon-bar"></span>
             </button>
             <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">Hipstacart</a>
           </div>
           <div id="navbar" class="navbar-collapse collapse">
             <form class="navbar-form navbar-left" role="search">
             <%= form_tag root_path, method: :get do %>
             <%= text_field_tag :search_text %>
             <%= submit_tag "Search", class: "btn btn-default" %>
           </form>
           <% end %>
             <form class="navbar-form navbar-right">
               <div class="form-group">
                 <input type="text" placeholder="Email" class="form-control">
               </div>
               <div class="form-group">
                 <input type="password" placeholder="Password" class="form-control">
               </div>
               <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success">Sign in</button>
               <a class="cartbutton" href="cart"><i class="fa fa-shopping-cart"></i></a>
              <a class="buttoncount" href="cart"> <%= @cart.cart_items.sum('quantity') %> </a>
             </form>
           </div><!--/.navbar-collapse -->
         </div>
       </nav>

       <!-- Main jumbotron for a primary marketing message or call to action -->
       <div class="jumbotron">
         <div class="container">
           <!-- <img src="logo.jpeg" height="55" width="55"> -->
           <h1>Hipstacart!<h3>... wear cool things before they're cool.</h3></h1>
           <br>
           <p>here you can find everything you will need to be a hipster! </p>
           <p><a>

         </div>
         <div class="pull-right">
            <%= link_to "What is a Hipster?", info_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg" %>
          </div>
       </div>
<HR WIDTH="60%">

          <div class="container">
            <% @products.each do |product| %>
              <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                <h2><%= product.name %></h2>
                <%= link_to product do %>
                  <%= image_tag product.photo.thumb, class: "img-responsive" %>
                <% end %>
              </div>
            <% end %>
          </div>


          <hr>


       <div class="container">
         <!-- Example row of columns -->
         <div class="row">
           <div class="col-md-4">
             <h2>Why Mustaches</h2>
             <p>The mustache has been a long lived theme in hipsterdom. If you want to be different from everyone else by looking the same as everyone... Get yourself some mustache wax.  </p>
             <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="http://www.chicagonow.com/lists-that-actually-matter/2011/03/top-10-things-hipsters-love/#image/10" role="button">View details &raquo;</a></p>
           </div>
           <div class="col-md-4">
             <h2>#1 hipster-ism</h2>
             <p>If you want to be a real hipster, make sure you deny that you are one. This way you'll make sure to embrace the irony of being one while claiming you're not. </p>
             <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="http://www.chicagonow.com/lists-that-actually-matter/2014/04/5-more-things-hipsters-love/#image/3" role="button">View details &raquo;</a></p>
          </div>
           <div class="col-md-4">
             <h2>Do you get it?</h2>
             <p>The thing that separates hipsters from the rest of us in society is that they just, you know, like, get it. They know how to save the environment and politics, and don't even get them started on what qualifies as good music. </p>
             <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="http://www.chicagonow.com/lists-that-actually-matter/2014/04/5-more-things-hipsters-love/#image/5" role="button">View details &raquo;</a></p>
           </div>
         </div>

         <hr>

